-- Vanguard Group posts inflows of $21.3 bln across its funds in November  
-- 
-- Wed Dec 03, 2014 04:10PM EST
-- None



NEW YORK, Dec 3 (Reuters) - The Vanguard Group posted inflows of $21.3 billion across its funds in November, including $7.6 billion into its bond funds, the firm said on Wednesday.

Vanguard said three of its top 10 months of cash flow into its bond funds have occurred in 2014.